zing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-weight: bold;\">3. 지원자격</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">  가. 2026-1학기 현재 본교 1학기~7학기(편입생은 1학기~3학기) 재학생</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">    ※ 정규 8학기(편입생은4학기) 이상 재학생, 휴학생, 수료생, 대학원생은 불가</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">    ※ 2026.8월 졸업 또는 수료 예정인 재학생 불가</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">  나. 지원대학 어학성적 및 기타 입학요건을 충족시키는 자</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">  다. 기타 해외 여행에 결격사유가 없는 자</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 굴림;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-weight: bold;\">4. 신청방법</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 16px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 굴림;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">가. nDRIMS 신청(학사행정 - [학생신청]신청함 - [국제교류]국제교류신청 - '2026/여름학기' 및 언어권 </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">'영어' 선택)</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 16px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 굴림;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">  ※ 수학계획서는 4,000자 내로 영어로 작성하여 엔드림스로 제출</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">   나. 1개 학교만 선택 가능</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span class=\"hnc_page_break\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.5em;\"> </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle2\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-weight: bold;\">5. 신청기간</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">: 2026. 3. 26.(목) ~ 3. 31.(화) 13:00까지</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span class=\"hnc_page_break\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.5em;\"> </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-weight: bold;\">5. 장학금 지급</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 16px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 굴림;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">가. 프로그램 참가 확정자 중, ‘장학금 수혜조건’ 충족하는 참가자에게 해외 단기연수 장학금 지급</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 16px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 굴림;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">  ※ 장학금 지급예정액 : 2,000,000원/인(유럽,미국), 1,000,000원/인(아시아) (재원: 대학혁신지원사업)</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 16px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 굴림;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">나. 장학금은 프로그램을 정상적으로 이수한 학생에게 연수 종료 후 지급하며, 프로그램 미수료 및 </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">중도포기 귀국자 등에는 미지급</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 16px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 굴림;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">다. 장학금액은 변경될 수 있으며, 장학금액 및 장학금 수혜를 위한 제출서류 및 유의사항은 합격자 </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">대상으로 별도 안내 예정</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 16px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 굴림;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">라. 장학금 수혜 조건</span></span></span></p>\n<div style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">    </span></span></span></div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; border: none; table-layout: fixed;'>\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n<td bgcolor=\"#fcf5e7\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 7px; overflow: hidden; width: 609px; height: 152px; border-width: 0.42525pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\"> ‣ 2026-1학기 본교 1학기~7학기(편입생은 1학기~3학기) 재학생</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">   </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">※ 정규 8학기(편입생은 4학기) 이상 재학생, 휴학생, 수료생, 대학원생은 불가</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">   ※ 2026.8월에 졸업예정자 및 수료예정자 불가</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\"> ‣ </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; line-height: 22.4px;\">2025학년도 동‧하계 해외 단기연수 장학금 수혜자 불가</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\"> ‣ 2026학년도 타 해외연수 장학(학생처 주관 해외탐방, 해외봉사 등 대학혁신지원사업 국고</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">   재원 장학) 수혜자 및 수혜예정자(참가예정자) 중복수급 불가</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\"> ‣ 기타 해외 여행에 결격사유가 없는 자</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"> </p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span class=\"hnc_page_break\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.5em;\"> </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; font-weight: bold;\">6. 평가방법</span></span></span></p>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; border: none; table-layout: fixed;'>\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n<td bgcolor=\"#fff7cc\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 7px; overflow: hidden; width: 239px; height: 25px; border-width: 0.42525pt 0.42525pt 0.42525pt 0.8505pt; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p class=\"HStyle2\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; letter-spacing: 0px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">구분</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td bgcolor=\"#fff7cc\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 7px; overflow: hidden; width: 399px; height: 25px; border-width: 0.42525pt; border-style: solid none solid solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p class=\"HStyle2\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\"; letter-spacing: 0px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><sp