, 0);\" valign=\"middle\">\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">ㆍ참가서류 평가 및 면접 실시</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕; letter-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">  </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">‣</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\"> </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">수학계획서(40%), 면접(60%) 평가</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; letter-spacing: -0.06em; font-weight: bold;\">7. 학점인정</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 26pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -26pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; letter-spacing: -0.06em;\"> 가. 소속학과 학점인정 결과에 따라 인정 가능한 범위 안에서 결정되며, 전공 또는 자선학점 여부 결정</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 26pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -26pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; letter-spacing: -0.06em;\"> 나. 프로그램 및 수강과목에 따라 학점인정이 불가할 수 있음</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 26pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -26pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span class=\"hnc_page_break\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.5em;\"> </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 26pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -26pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; letter-spacing: -0.06em; font-weight: bold;\">8. 유의사항</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 26pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -26pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; letter-spacing: -0.06em;\"> 가. 파견을 위해 발생되는 수업료, 행정수수료, 항공권, 숙소비 등은 개인 부담 비용임</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 26pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -26pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; letter-spacing: -0.06em;\"> 나. 현지 사정 및 자매대학교 사정으로 인해 프로그램이 취소될 수 있음</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 26pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -26pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; letter-spacing: -0.06em;\"> 다. 동국대학교에서 선발하더라도 자매대학에서 선발하지 않을 수 있으며, 자매대학 입학허가서를 받아야 최종선발이 확정됨</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 26pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -26pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; letter-spacing: -0.06em;\"> 라. 2026 하계 해외 단기 연수프로그램 중복지원 불가(영어권 및 타 언어권 프로그램 합격(합격을 포기한 경우에도) 후 중복 지원 불가)</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 26pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -26pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; letter-spacing: -0.06em;\"> 마. 프로그램에 참가하여 이수하더라도, 학적상태 변동(졸업, 수료 등), 타 해외연수 참가에 따른 장학금 수혜 등,</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 26pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -26pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; letter-spacing: -0.06em;\">     해외 단기연수 장학금 수혜조건을 충족시키지 못하는 사안이 확인되는 경우에는 장학금 미지급</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 26pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -26pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"> </p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 26pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -26pt; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; letter-spacing: -0.06em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">9. 문의</span>: 신공학관 9층 글로벌교류팀 (02-2260-3464 / outbound1@dongguk.edu)</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: tahoma;\"><span class=\"hnc_page_break\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-spacing: -0.5em;\"> </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 21.3333px; font-size: 10p